/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fknowledge-library.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fknowledge-library.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-l from-transparent to-[#F6F4F1]/72\"></div></div><header class=\"p-8 text-right lg:p-12\"><nav class=\"mb-5 text-xs font-bold text-muted\"><a class=\"hover:text-gold\" href=\"/\">الرئيسية</a><span class=\"mx-2 text-gold\">›</span><span>شروط الاستخدام</span></nav><h1 class=\"font-display text-5xl font-extrabold leading-tight text-[#1D1916]\">شروط الاستخدام</h1><p class=\"mt-5 max-w-xl text-base font-bold leading-8 text-muted\">تنظم هذه الشروط والأحكام استخدام منصة مهابة وخدماتها المتعلقة بالأصول العقارية والمساهمات العقارية والخدمات العقارية.</p><p class=\"mt-5 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-extrabold text-[#A7815E]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-calendar-days h-4 w-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M8 2v4\"></path><path d=\"M16 2v4\"></path><rect width=\"18\" height=\"18\" x=\"3\" y=\"4\" rx=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M3 10h18\"></path><path d=\"M8 14h.01\"></path><path d=\"M12 14h.01\"></path><path d=\"M16 14h.01\"></path><path d=\"M8 18h.01\"></path><path d=\"M12 18h.01\"></path><path d=\"M16 18h.01\"></path></svg>آخر تحديث: 12 مايو 2026</p></header></div></div></section><section class=\"section-compact pt-0\"><div class=\"container-page grid gap-3 md:grid-cols-5\"><a class=\"flex h-16 items-center justify-center gap-3 rounded-md border border-line bg-white/72 px-4 text-sm font-extrabold text-navy transition hover:border-[#A7815E]/55 hover:text-[#8F6B4C]\" href=\"#legal-section-1\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-handshake h-5 w-5 text-[#A7815E]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m11 17 2 2a1 1 0 1 0 3-3\"></path><path d=\"m14 14 2.5 2.5a1 1 0 1 0 3-3l-3.88-3.88a3 3 0 0 0-4.24 0l-.88.88a1 1 0 1 1-3-3l2.81-2.81a5.79 5.79 0 0 1 7.06-.87l.47.28a2 2 0 0 0 1.42.25L21 4\"></path><path d=\"m21 3 1 11h-2\"></path><path d=\"M3 3 2 14l6.5 6.5a1 1 0 1 0 3-3\"></path><path d=\"M3 4h8\"></path></svg>قبول الشروط</a><a class=\"flex h-16 items-center justify-center gap-3 rounded-md border border-line bg-white/72 px-4 text-sm font-extrabold text-navy transition hover:border-[#A7815E]/55 hover:text-[#8F6B4C]\" href=\"#legal-section-3\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-user-round h-5 w-5 text-[#A7815E]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"8\" r=\"5\"></circle><path d=\"M20 21a8 8 0 0 0-16 0\"></path></svg>الحسابات</a><a class=\"flex h-16 items-center justify-center gap-3 rounded-md border border-line bg-white/72 px-4 text-sm font-extrabold text-navy transition hover:border-[#A7815E]/55 hover:text-[#8F6B4C]\" href=\"#legal-section-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-laptop h-5 w-5 text-[#A7815E]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M18 5a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v8.526a2 2 0 0 0 .212.897l1.068 2.127a1 1 0 0 1-.9 1.45H3.62a1 1 0 0 1-.9-1.45l1.068-2.127A2 2 0 0 0 4 15.526V7a2 2 0 0 1 2-2z\"></path><path d=\"M20.054 15.987H3.946\"></path></svg>استخدام المنصة</a><a class=\"flex h-16 items-center justify-center gap-3 rounded-md border border-line bg-white/72 px-4 text-sm font-extrabold text-navy transition hover:border-[#A7815E]/55 hover:text-[#8F6B4C]\" href=\"#legal-section-3\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield-check h-5 w-5 text-[#A7815E]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z\"></path><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg>المسؤولية</a><a class=\"flex h-16 items-center justify-center gap-3 rounded-md border border-line bg-white/72 px-4 text-sm font-extrabold text-navy transition hover:border-[#A7815E]/55 hover:text-[#8F6B4C]\" href=\"#legal-section-11\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-phone h-5 w-5 text-[#A7815E]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M13.832 16.568a1 1 0 0 0 1.213-.303l.355-.465A2 2 0 0 1 17 15h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v3a2 2 0 0 1-2 2A18 18 0 0 1 2 4a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v3a2 2 0 0 1-.8 1.6l-.468.351a1 1 0 0 0-.292 1.233 14 14 0 0 0 6.392 6.384\"></path></svg>التواصل معنا</a></div></section><section class=\"section-compact pt-0\"><div class=\"container-page\"><div class=\"overflow-hidden rounded-lg border border-line shadow-[0_12px_26px_rgb(24_23_21/0.035)]\"><section id=\"legal-section-1\" class=\"scroll-mt-28 grid gap-5 border-b border-line bg-white/68 p-6 text-right last:border-b-0 md:grid-cols-[1fr_260px]\"><div class=\"text-sm font-bold leading-9 text-muted\"><p>باستخدامك منصة مهابة فإنك توافق على الالتزام بجميع الشروط والأحكام الواردة في هذه الصفحة كما يحق لمهابة تحديث أي من هذه الشروط في أي وقت.</p></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-end gap-4 md:justify-start\"><h2 class=\"font-display text-2xl font-extrabold text-[#1D1916]\">1. مقدمة</h2><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-file-text h-12 w-12 shrink-0 stroke-[1.25] text-[#A7815E]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M6 22a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V4a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h8a2.4 2.4 0 0 1 1.704.706l3.588 3.588A2.4 2.4 0 0 1 20 8v12a2 2 0 0 1-2 2z\"></path><path d=\"M14 2v5a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h5\"></path><path d=\"M10 9H8\"></path><path d=\"M16 13H8\"></path><path d=\"M16 17H8\"></path></svg></div></section><section id=\"legal-section-2\" class=\"scroll-mt-28 grid gap-5 border-b border-line bg-white/68 p-6 text-right last:border-b-0 md:grid-cols-[1fr_260px]\"><div class=\"text-sm font-bold leading-9 text-muted\"><p>المستخدم هو كل شخص يقوم بالوصول إلى المنصة أو استخدامها. المنصة هي موقع وخدمات مهابة لإدارة الأصول والمساهمات والخدمات العقارية.</p></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-end gap-4 md:justify-start\"><h2 class=\"font-display text-2xl font-extrabold text-[#1D1916]\">2. التعريفات</h2><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-file-text h-12 w-12 shrink-0 stroke-[1.25] text-[#A7815E]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M6 22a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V4a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h8a2.4 2.4 0 0 1 1.704.706l3.588 3.588A2.4 2.4 0 0 1 20 8v12a2 2 0 0 1-2 2z\"></path><path d=\"M14 2v5a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h5\"></path><path d=\"M10 9H8\"></path><path d=\"M16 13H8\"></path><path d=\"M16 17H8\"></path></svg></div></section><section id=\"legal-section-3\" class=\"scroll-mt-28 grid gap-5 border-b border-line bg-white/68 p-6 text-right last:border-b-0 md:grid-cols-[1fr_260px]\"><div class=\"text-sm font-bold leading-9 text-muted\"><p>يلتزم المستخدم بتقديم معلومات صحيحة ودقيقة عند إنشاء الحساب، والمحافظة على سرية بيانات الدخول وتحمل المسؤولية عن أي نشاط يتم عبر حسابه.</p></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-end gap-4 md:justify-start\"><h2 class=\"font-display text-2xl font-extrabold text-[#1D1916]\">3. الحسابات</h2><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-user-round h-12 w-12 shrink-0 stroke-[1.25] text-[#A7815E]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"8\" r=\"5\"></circle><path d=\"M20 21a8 8 0 0 0-16 0\"></path></svg></div></section><section id=\"legal-section-4\" class=\"scroll-mt-28 grid gap-5 border-b border-line bg-white/68 p-6 text-right last:border-b-0 md:grid-cols-[1fr_260px]\"><div class=\"text-sm font-bold leading-9 text-muted\"><p>يجب استخدام المنصة للأغراض المشروعة فقط وبما لا يتعارض مع الأنظمة واللوائح المعمول بها في المملكة العربية السعودية.</p></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-end gap-4 md:justify-start\"><h2 class=\"font-display text-2xl font-extrabold text-[#1D1916]\">4. استخدام المنصة</h2><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-laptop h-12 w-12 shrink-0 stroke-[1.25] text-[#A7815E]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M18 5a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v8.526a2 2 0 0 0 .212.897l1.068 2.127a1 1 0 0 1-.9 1.45H3.62a1 1 0 0 1-.9-1.45l1.068-2.127A2 2 0 0 0 4 15.526V7a2 2 0 0 1 2-2z\"></path><path d=\"M20.054 15.987H3.946\"></path></svg></div></section><section id=\"legal-section-5\" class=\"scroll-mt-28 grid gap-5 border-b border-line bg-white/68 p-6 text-right last:border-b-0 md:grid-cols-[1fr_260px]\"><div class=\"text-sm font-bold leading-9 text-muted\"><p>يتحمل المستخدم مسؤولية صحة ودقة البيانات والمستندات المضافة للأصول العقارية، ولا تضمن مهابة صحة البيانات المقدمة من المستخدمين.</p></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-end gap-4 md:justify-start\"><h2 class=\"font-display text-2xl font-extrabold text-[#1D1916]\">5. الأصول العقارية</h2><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-building2 lucide-building-2 h-12 w-12 shrink-0 stroke-[1.25] text-[#A7815E]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 12h4\"></path><path d=\"M10 8h4\"></path><path d=\"M14 21v-3a2 2 0 0 0-4 0v3\"></path><path d=\"M6 10H4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v7a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h16a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V9a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-2\"></path><path d=\"M6 21V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h8a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v16\"></path></svg></div></section><section id=\"legal-section-6\" class=\"scroll-mt-28 grid gap-5 border-b border-line bg-white/68 p-6 text-right last:border-b-0 md:grid-cols-[1fr_260px]\"><div class=\"text-sm font-bold leading-9 text-muted\"><p>تعرض المنصة معلومات المساهمات العقارية والفرص الاستثمارية لأغراض الاطلاع فقط، ويجب على المستخدم اتخاذ قراراته بناء على دراسة خاصة.</p></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-end gap-4 md:justify-start\"><h2 class=\"font-display text-2xl font-extrabold text-[#1D1916]\">6. المساهمات العقارية</h2><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-scale h-12 w-12 shrink-0 stroke-[1.25] text-[#A7815E]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 3v18\"></path><path d=\"m19 8 3 8a5 5 0 0 1-6 0zV7\"></path><path d=\"M3 7h1a17 17 0 0 0 8-2 17 17 0 0 0 8 2h1\"></path><path d=\"m5 8 3 8a5 5 0 0 1-6 0zV7\"></path><path d=\"M7 21h10\"></path></svg></div></section><section id=\"legal-section-7\" class=\"scroll-mt-28 grid gap-5 border-b border-line bg-white/68 p-6 text-right last:border-b-0 md:grid-cols-[1fr_260px]\"><div class=\"text-sm font-bold leading-9 text-muted\"><p>يتم تنفيذ الخدمات العقارية وفق نطاق كل خدمة وشروطها الخاصة، وقد تتطلب بعض الخدمات مراجعات أو مستندات إضافية قبل التنفيذ.</p></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-end gap-4 md:justify-start\"><h2 class=\"font-display text-2xl font-extrabold text-[#1D1916]\">7. الخدمات العقارية</h2><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-pen-line h-12 w-12 shrink-0 stroke-[1.25] text-[#A7815E]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M13 21h8\"></path><path d=\"M21.174 6.812a1 1 0 0 0-3.986-3.987L3.842 16.174a2 2 0 0 0-.5.83l-1.321 4.352a.5.5 0 0 0 .623.622l4.353-1.32a2 2 0 0 0 .83-.497z\"></path></svg></div></section><section id=\"legal-section-8\" class=\"scroll-mt-28 grid gap-5 border-b border-line bg-white/68 p-6 text-right last:border-b-0 md:grid-cols-[1fr_260px]\"><div class=\"text-sm font-bold leading-9 text-muted\"><p>جميع الحقوق المتعلقة بالمنصة والشعارات والمحتوى والنصوص والرسومات والصور محفوظة لمهابة، ولا يجوز استخدامها أو نسخها دون إذن كتابي مسبق.</p></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-end gap-4 md:justify-start\"><h2 class=\"font-display text-2xl font-extrabold text-[#1D1916]\">8. الملكية الفكرية</h2><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-key-round h-12 w-12 shrink-0 stroke-[1.25] text-[#A7815E]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M2.586 17.414A2 2 0 0 0 2 18.828V21a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h3a1 1 0 0 0 1-1v-1a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h1a1 1 0 0 0 1-1v-1a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h.172a2 2 0 0 0 1.414-.586l.814-.814a6.5 6.5 0 1 0-4-4z\"></path><circle cx=\"16.5\" cy=\"7.5\" r=\".5\" fill=\"currentColor\"></circle></svg></div></section><section id=\"legal-section-9\" class=\"scroll-mt-28 grid gap-5 border-b border-line bg-white/68 p-6 text-right last:border-b-0 md:grid-cols-[1fr_260px]\"><div class=\"text-sm font-bold leading-9 text-muted\"><p>لا تتحمل مهابة أي مسؤولية عن أي خسائر مباشرة أو غير مباشرة تنتج عن استخدام المنصة أو الاعتماد على المعلومات المنشورة أو الخدمات المقدمة.</p></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-end gap-4 md:justify-start\"><h2 class=\"font-display text-2xl font-extrabold text-[#1D1916]\">9. حدود المسؤولية</h2><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield-check h-12 w-12 shrink-0 stroke-[1.25] text-[#A7815E]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z\"></path><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg></div></section><section id=\"legal-section-10\" class=\"scroll-mt-28 grid gap-5 border-b border-line bg-white/68 p-6 text-right last:border-b-0 md:grid-cols-[1fr_260px]\"><div class=\"text-sm font-bold leading-9 text-muted\"><p>يجوز لمهابة تعديل هذه الشروط والأحكام في أي وقت، وسيتم إشعار المستخدمين بالتحديثات عند نشرها على المنصة.</p></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-end gap-4 md:justify-start\"><h2 class=\"font-display text-2xl font-extrabold text-[#1D1916]\">10. تعديل الشروط</h2><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-pen-line h-12 w-12 shrink-0 stroke-[1.25] text-[#A7815E]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M13 21h8\"></path><path d=\"M21.174 6.812a1 1 0 0 0-3.986-3.987L3.842 16.174a2 2 0 0 0-.5.83l-1.321 4.352a.5.5 0 0 0 .623.622l4.353-1.32a2 2 0 0 0 .83-.497z\"></path></svg></div></section><section id=\"legal-section-11\" class=\"scroll-mt-28 grid gap-5 border-b border-line bg-white/68 p-6 text-right last:border-b-0 md:grid-cols-[1fr_260px]\"><div class=\"text-sm font-bold leading-9 text-muted\"><p>لأي استفسارات أو ملاحظات تتعلق بهذه الشروط يمكنكم التواصل معنا عبر وسائل الاتصال الرسمية أدناه.</p></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-end gap-4 md:justify-start\"><h2 class=\"font-display text-2xl font-extrabold text-[#1D1916]\">11. التواصل معنا</h2><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-headphones h-12 w-12 shrink-0 stroke-[1.25] text-[#A7815E]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M3 14h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v3a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-7a9 9 0 0 1 18 0v7a2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-1a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-3a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h3\"></path></svg></div></section></div></div></section><section class=\"section-compact pt-0\"><div class=\"container-page grid gap-3 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4\"><article class=\"grid min-h-24 grid-cols-[1fr_48px] items-center gap-3 rounded-lg border border-line bg-white/72 p-4 text-right\"><div><h3 class=\"font-display text-base font-extrabold text-navy\">الجوال</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-xs font-bold text-muted\">0510515010</p></div><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-phone h-9 w-9 text-[#A7815E]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M13.832 16.568a1 1 0 0 0 1.213-.303l.355-.465A2 2 0 0 1 17 15h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v3a2 2 0 0 1-2 2A18 18 0 0 1 2 4a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v3a2 2 0 0 1-.8 1.6l-.468.351a1 1 0 0 0-.292 1.233 14 14 0 0 0 6.392 6.384\"></path></svg></article><article class=\"grid min-h-24 grid-cols-[1fr_48px] items-center gap-3 rounded-lg border border-line bg-white/72 p-4 text-right\"><div><h3 class=\"font-display text-base font-extrabold text-navy\">البريد الإلكتروني</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-xs font-bold text-muted\">info@mahabah.sa</p></div><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-mail h-9 w-9 text-[#A7815E]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m22 7-8.991 5.727a2 2 0 0 1-2.009 0L2 7\"></path><rect x=\"2\" y=\"4\" width=\"20\" height=\"16\" rx=\"2\"></rect></svg></article><article class=\"grid min-h-24 grid-cols-[1fr_48px] items-center gap-3 rounded-lg border border-line bg-white/72 p-4 text-right\"><div><h3 class=\"font-display text-base font-extrabold text-navy\">الموقع الإلكتروني</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-xs font-bold text-muted\">mahabah.sa</p></div><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-earth h-9 w-9 text-[#A7815E]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M21.54 15H17a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v4.54\"></path><path d=\"M7 3.34V5a3 3 0 0 0 3 3a2 2 0 0 1 2 2c0 1.1.9 2 2 2a2 2 0 0 0 2-2c0-1.1.9-2 2-2h3.17\"></path><path d=\"M11 21.95V18a2 2 0 0 0-2-2a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-1a2 2 0 0 0-2-2H2.05\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle></svg></article><article class=\"grid min-h-24 grid-cols-[1fr_48px] items-center gap-3 rounded-lg border border-line bg-white/72 p-4 text-right\"><div><h3 class=\"font-display text-base font-extrabold text-navy\">الرياض</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-xs font-bold text-muted\">المملكة العربية السعودية</p></div><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-map-pin h-9 w-9 text-[#A7815E]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 10c0 4.993-5.539 10.193-7.399 11.799a1 1 0 0 1-1.202 0C9.539 20.193 4 14.993 4 10a8 8 0 0 1 16 0\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"10\" r=\"3\"></circle></svg></article></div></section><section class=\"pb-7 pt-3\"><div class=\"landing-container\"><div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-lg border border-line bg-[#f7f2ec] px-5 py-6 shadow-card md:px-8\" style=\"opacity:0;filter:blur(8px);transform:translateY(18px)\"><div class=\"pointer-events-none absolute inset-0\"><img alt=\"رسم معماري لأصل عقاري\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-contain object-left-bottom opacity-95 grayscale-[8%] sepia-[8%]\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Ffinal-cta-map-building.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Ffinal-cta-map-building.png&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Ffinal-cta-map-building.png&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Ffinal-cta-map-building.png&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Ffinal-cta-map-building.png&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Ffinal-cta-map-building.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Ffinal-cta-map-building.png&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Ffinal-cta-map-building.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Ffinal-cta-map-building.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/></div><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-[#f7f2ec]/82 to-[#f7f2ec]/98\"></div><div class=\"relative z-10 grid items-center gap-5 lg:grid-cols-[280px_1fr_auto]\"><div class=\"relative hidden h-28 lg:block\"></div><div class=\"text-right\"><h2 class=\"font-display text-2xl font-extrabold text-[#1D1916] md:text-3xl\">لديك أصل عقاري وترغب في تطويره أو استثماره؟</h2><p class=\"mt-3 max-w-2xl text-sm font-bold leading-8 text-muted\">انضم إلى منصة مهابة وابدأ رحلتك نحو تحويل أصولك العقارية إلى مساهمات عقارية منظمة وفق معايير الحوكمة والشفافية والامتثال.</p></div><a class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center border border-transparent font-semibold tra